text.tspan: Keep your finger on the screen to
Use the sprint button in the upper left to
Approach sharks from behind to ride them
Once you mount a shark keep your finger
on the shark to continue riding
If you can not keep your finger on the
shark you will be thrown off
Riding a shark for a sufficient amount
of time will cause it to disappear
Powered by LibGDX from Badlogic Games
